id: pm-xpkt
title: "GH-416: Windows nightly validate linked-artifact prune classification"
description: "Fix GitHub issue #416: scheduled Nightly Validation run 28573486269 failed on windows-latest / Node 24 because validate-command.spec.ts expected an overlong linked artifact path to be treated as unreadable, but Windows classified it as a missing linked path and included it in prune-missing output. Reuse existing validate linked-artifact lineage (pm-0v2m, pm-k2n4) and Windows nightly lineage (pm-83rt, pm-2kkl) without reopening terminal work. Acceptance: Windows-compatible regression coverage, focused validate tests, full quality gates, temp-dir smoke, GH issue/PR evidence."
type: Issue
status: in_progress
priority: 1
tags[5]: "area:ci","area:validate",github-issue-416,reliability,windows
